column19:
My goals are threefold:

To get a solid understanding of the models behind image, text, and video generation—and become proficient in tools such as LangChain, ComfyUI, and other GenAI frameworks that enable rapid prototyping and deployment;

To bridge my product and business understanding with strong development skills—so I can either lead AI transformation within enterprises or build independent tech products going forward.

To build and deploy at least 2–3 real-world AI-powered apps that I can showcase in a portfolio;

Ultimately, I want this cohort to sharpen my execution capabilities and open up higher-impact roles—whether in AI consulting, product ownership, or even founding a tech-first startup.
